We are working hard to bring you new and exciting features. This version includes new features and enhancements that will make KalamTime a better way to communicate with your loved ones. Now you can do private chat with your loved ones. Enable private chat by opening profile page of your contact and then click on the switch next to Enable Private Chat option. No messages in private chats are saved on the KalamTime server. All private messages are stored only on the device where you started the private chat. We have improved the experience of Chat screen. Now scrolling through messages is even smoother. We have killed some bugs to make sure that KalamTime is a nicer place to communicate
